HEADWORD: hard-nosed
<hw>hard-nosed</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>facing reality squarely; guided
by practical experience and observation rather than theory; tough and
pragmatic; <as>as, a <ex>hard-nosed</ex> businessman</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> down-to-earth, hardheaded, practical,
pragmatic.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

